icalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-childrens-lies-challenging-parenting-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Now%2C%20Tea%20For%20Rs%2010%20At%20Kolkata%20Airport%2C%20Raghav%20Chadha%20Says%20%26quot%3BChange%20Brewing%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20said%20his%20efforts%20have%20led%20to%20lowering%20of%20food%20and%20water%20prices%20at%20airports%20after%20the%20government%20launched%20affordable%20Udaan%20Yatri%20Cafe.%20Mr%20Chadha%20had%20in%20parliament%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20overpriced%20food%20and%20beverages%20at%20airports%2C%20prompting%20the%20government%20to%20launch%20the%20Udaan%20Yatri%20Cafe%2C%20Mr%20Chadha%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Udaan%20Yatri%20Cafe%20has%20been%20launched%20at%20Kolkata%20airport%2C%20offering%20water%2C%20tea%2C%20and%20snacks%20at%20reasonable%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chadha%20reminded%20the%20government%20of%20its%20promise%20to%20make%20air%20travel%20affordable%2C%20highlighting%20that%20rising%20costs%20have%20made%20it%20challenging%20for%20the%20common%20people%20to%20fly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGlad%20to%20see%20the%20change%20brewing!%20After%20I%20highlighted%20the%20issue%20of%20food%20affordability%20at%20airports%20during%20this%20Winter%20Session%20of%20Parliament%2C%20tea%20prices%20at%20Kolkata%20Airport%20have%20been%20reduced.%20This%20is%20a%20win%20for%20us%20citizens%2C%20and%20I%20take%20pride%20in%20being%20the%20catalyst%20for%20this%20change.%20Hope%20more%20airports%20will%20follow%20this%20example%20and%20price%20food%20items%20more%20reasonably.%20Which%20issues%20should%20I%20raise%20in%20the%20next%20session%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20MP%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EGlad%20t