wed%20the%2038-year-old%20to%20now%20become%20the%20first%20person%20to%20achieve%20a%20rather%20unique%20thing.%20Ashwin%20is%20among%2014%20Indian%20players%20to%20have%20made%20more%20than%20100%20Test%20appearances%20for%20India%2C%20and%20one%20of%2078%20players%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20game%20to%20do%20so.%20However%2C%20Ashwin%20will%20go%20down%20as%20the%20first-ever%20player%20in%20the%20147%20years%20since%20Test%20cricket%20began%20with%20100%20or%20more%20Test%20caps%20who%20has%20never%20played%20a%20single%20match%20against%20Pakistan.%20While%20Ashwin%20is%20the%20first%20in%20the%20list%2C%20he%20could%20soon%20have%20two%20of%20his%20teammates%20join%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20frosty%20relations%20with%20Pakistan%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20world%20of%20cricket%20has%20seen%20the%20two%20nations%20not%20play%20a%20single%20Test%20match%20against%20each%20other%20since%20December%202007.%20With%20Ashwin's%20career%20beginning%20after%20that%2C%20he%20became%20the%20first-ever%20player%20to%20retire%20with%20more%20than%20100%20Test%20caps%2C%20but%20having%20never%20played%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20could%20soon%20be%20joined%20on%20the%20list%20by%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Cheteshwar%20Pujara%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F897-cheteshwar-pujara-playerprofile%5C%22%3ECheteshwar%20Pujara%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20list.%20Kohli%20and%20Pujara%20have%20both%20never%20faced%20Pakistan%2C%20despite%20registering%20more%20than%20100%20Test%20matches%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20way%20things%20have%20turned%20out%20regarding%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20neither%20country%20will%20tour%20each%20other%20in%20any%20form%20of%20cricket%20till%20at%20least%202027%2C%20by%20which%20time%2C%20both%20Kohli%20and%20Pujara%20may%20have%20called%20time%20on%20their%20own%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20possibility%20of%20Kohli%20or%20Pujara%20playing%20against%20Pakistan%20would%20be%20a%20potential%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20final%2C%20which%20would%20take%20place%20in%20a%20neutral%20venue.%20With%20Pakistan%20out%20of%20the%20race%20in%20the%202023-25%20cycle%2C%20such%20a%20scenario%20could%20only%20take%20place%20from%20the%20next%20cycle%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20any%20India-Pakistan%20Test%20encounter%20is%20highly%20unlikely%20until%20at%20least%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%20will%20next%20square%20off%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20at%20a%20neutral%20venue%2C%20despite%20Pakistan%20being%20the%20tournament's%20original%20hosts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734877920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F3c5cevd_r-ashwin-afp_625x300_19_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ffirst-time-in-147-years-ravichandran-ashwin-sets-unique-pakistan-record-after-retirement-7307877%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin's%20sudden%20retirement%20has%20made%20him%20the%20first%20player%20in%20cricket%20history%20to%20achieve%20something%20rather%20unique.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ffirst-time-in-147-years-ravichandran-ashwin-sets-unique-pakistan-record-after-retirement-7307877%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20Safe%20Car%20Enough%3F%20Volvo%20Crash%20That%20Killed%20CEO%2C%20Family%20Sparks%20Big%20Question%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20chilling%20crash%20of%20a%20Volvo%20SUV%20near%20Bengaluru%20yesterday%2C%20which%20claimed%20six%20lives%2C%20has%20sparked%20a%20conversation%20on%20how%20safe%20cars%20may%20not%20make%20a%20difference%20unless%20our%20roads%20are%20made%20safer.%20The%20Volvo%20XC90%2C%20considered%20the%20gold%20standard%20in%20car%20safety%2C%20was%20crushed%20by%20a%20container%20truck%20that%20jumped%20the%20divider%20on%20the%20Nelmangala-Tumkuru%20highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Chandram%20Yegapagol%20(48)%2C%20his%20wife%20Gourabai%20(42)%2C%20his%20son%20Gyan%20(16)%2C%20daughter%20Deeksha%20(12)%20sister-in-law%20Vijayalakshmi%20(36)%20and%20Vijayalakshmi's%20daughter%20Arya%20(6).%20Chandram%20Yegapagol%20was%20the%20managing%20director%20and%20CEO%20of%20IAST%20Software%20Solutions%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20automotive%20solutions%20firm%2C%20and%20had%20reportedly%20bought%20the%20SUV%20just%20two%20months%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20family%20was%20going%20to%20Sangli%20in%20neighbouring%20Maharashtra%20to%20meet%20Chandram's%20father.%20Police%20have%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fbengaluru-it-firm-ceo-5-kin-killed-as-container-truck-falls-on-suv%2Farticleshow%2F116554082.cms%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20was%20driving%20safely%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20at%20fault%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArif%2C%20the%20driver%20of%20the%20container%20truck%2C%20who%20suffered%20injuries%20in%20the%20accident%2C%20has%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20heavy%20vehicle%20jumped%20the%20divider%20while%20trying%20to%20save%20a%20car%20that%20stopped%20suddenly%20on%20the%20highway.%20%26quot%3BA%20car%20in%20front%20of%20me%20hit%20the%20brakes%20suddenly.%20When%20I%20hit%20the%20brakes%2C%20the%20truck%20kept%20going%20forward.%20To%20save%20the%20car%2C%20I%20swerved%20to%20the%20right%20and%20the%20truck%20jumped%20the%20divider%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20truck%20then%20hit%20the%20milk%20truck%20before%20crushing%20the%20Volvo%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20said%20he%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20six%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20accident.%20He%20said%20the%20truck%20was%20transporting%20aluminum.%20It%20must%20be%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20is%20always%20difficult%20for%20loaded%20heavy%20vehicles%20to%20stop%20instantly%20because%20of%20their%20weight.%20This%20makes%20panic%20braking%20risky.%20The%20driver%2C%20Arif%2C%20has%20been%20booked%20for%20rash%20driving%20and%20death%20by%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accident%20has%20sparked%20a%20conversation%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20users%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20safest%20of%20cars%20cannot%20save%20lives%20unless%20others%20on%20the%20road%20are%20driving%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriveSmart%2C%20a%20handle%20promoting%20safe%20driving%2C%20shared%20shocking%20pictures%20from%20the%20accident%20site.%20%26quot%3BThis%20pic%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20being%20safer%20on%20the%20road%20is%20not%20achieved%20by%20a%20safer%20car%20alone.%20Safe%20Roads%20%2B%20Safe%20Driver%20%2B%20Safe%20Car%3A%20All%20three%20are%20essential%20for%20safety.%20All%20the%20passengers%20in%20this%20Volvo%20lost%20lives%20in%20this%20car%20which%20supposedly%20went%20through%20all%20types%20of%20testing%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20pic%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20being%20safer%20on%20the%20road%20is%20not%20achieved%20by%20a%20safer%20car%20alone.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSafe%20Roads%20%2B%20Safe%20Driver%20%2B%20Safe%20Car%20--%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAll%20three%20are%20essential%20for%20safety.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAll%20the%20passengers%20in%20this%20Volvo%20lost%20lives%20in%20this%20car%20which%20supposedly%20went%20through%20all%20types%20of%20testing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7p52rs2btF%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F7p52rs2btF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20DriveSmart%F0%9F%9B%A1%EF%B8%8F%20(%40DriveSmart_IN)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDriveSmart_IN%2Fstatus%2F1870419794266071281%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20users%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20Volvo%20makes%20very%20safe%20vehicles%2C%20it%20is%20impossible%20for%20a%20car%20to%20withstand%20the%20weight%20of%20a%20container%20loaded%20with%20aluminum.%20Others%20have%20tagged%20Union%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20to%20bring%20stricter%20rules%20to%20ensure%20road%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20police%20officer%20CK%20Baba%20has%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fbengaluru%2Fsix-cranes-brought-to-clear-accident-debris-at-bengaluru-nh-drivers-cleaners-aide-rescuers-3328269%5C%22%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20six%20cranes%20had%20to%20be%20brought%20in%20to%20remove%20the%20heavily%20loaded%20truck%20from%20over%20the%20car.%20Then%20the%20bodies%20of%20the%20family%20members%20were%20brought%20out%20one%20by%20one%20from%20the%20crushed%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20discussion%20on%20India's%20accident%20deaths%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Winter%20Session%2C%20Mr%20Gadkari%20said%20he%20has%20to%20hide%20his%20face%20at%20international%20conferences%20on%20road%20accidents.%20Referring%20to%20his%20target%20to%20reduce%20accidents%20by%20half%20when%20he%20took%20charge%20of%20the%20ministry%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BForget%20about%20reducing%20the%20number%20of%20accidents%2C%20I%20have%20no%20hesitation%20to%20admit%20that%20it%20has%20been%20increased.%20When%20I%20go%20to%20attend%20international%20conferences%20where%20there%20is%20a%20discussion%20on%20road%20accidents%2C%20I%20try%20to%20hide%20my%20face.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20that%20society%20has%20to%20change%20and%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20has%20to%20be%20respected%20if%20accidents%20have%20to%20be%20prevented.%