l%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20would%20mitigate%20some%20of%20the%20holiday%20stress.%20However%2C%20marrying%20into%20a%20big%20family%20like%20I%20did%2C%20I%20was%20still%20worried%20our%20celebration%20as%20a%20newlywed%20couple%20would%20get%20lost%20in%20the%20holiday%20chaos.%20This%20is%20without%20any%20fault%20to%20my%20amazing%20new%20family%3B%20it%20simply%20can't%20be%20helped.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20of%20their%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhaving-holiday-traditions-makes-parenting-easier-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efamily%20traditions%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20also%20different%20from%20my%20own.%20For%20example%2C%20they%20like%20to%20celebrate%20on%20Christmas%20Day%2C%20while%20I%20love%20the%20magic%20of%20a%20sparkling%20Christmas%20Eve.%20I%20can%20still%20bring%20traditions%20to%20their%20family%2C%20like%20decorating%20gingerbread%20houses%2C%20which%20I've%20done%20every%20year.%20Part%20of%20the%20original%20excitement%20toward%20the%20holiday%20was%20thinking%20about%20all%20the%20family%20traditions%20we%20would%20create%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20took%20me%20a%20long%20time%20to%20voice%20my%20concerns%20to%20my%20wife%2C%20worried%20I%20was%20overthinking%20it%20or%20wanting%20too%20much%20attention%20to%20still%20be%20on%20us.%20After%20all%2C%20we%20got%20married%20four%20months%20ago.%20However%2C%20my%20fears%20ended%20up%20being%20unfounded%20because%2C%20like%20the%20loving%20wife%20she%20is%2C%20Taryn%20listened%20and%20asked%20me%20what%20would%20make%20our%20holiday%20feel%20special.%20The%20truth%20was%2C%20I%20didn't%20know.%20Though%20I%20had%20all%20these%20expectations%20that%20this%20Christmas%20was%20supposed%20to%20feel%20different%2C%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20make%20that%20happen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20to%20get%20real%20with%20myself%20and%20understand%20that%2C%20just%20like%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplanned-wedding-never-happened-not-doing-it-again-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eplanning%20a%20wedding%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20putting%20too%20much%20pressure%20on%20yourself%20is%20the%20fastest%20way%20to%20steal%20the%20joy%20out%20of%20the%20process.%20Letting%20go%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20making%20things%20perfect%20allows%20me%20to%20focus%20on%20what%20truly%20matters%3A%20creating%20memories%20with%20my%20wife.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22013fc98f-587c-4ea8-a38a-3b5e32633a18%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20creating%20memories%20together%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20how%20do%20you%20go%20about%20making%20a%20newlywed%20Christmas%20as%20memorable%20as%20possible%3F%20We%20started%20with%20Christmas%20cards.%20Since%20we%20had%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicro-weddings-are-way-better-cheaper-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esmall%20wedding%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20not%20everyone%20in%20our%20life%20got%20to%20celebrate%20with%20us.%20Sending%20out%20Christmas%20cards%20we%20made%20together%20to%20those%20who%20are%20important%20to%20us%20helped%20us%20share%20our%20love%20%E2%80%94%20and%20our%20wedding%20photos.%20Speaking%20of%20wedding%20photos%2C%20there's%20no%20better%20Christmas%20gift%20for%20our%20family%20than%20a%20photo%20album%20to%20remember%20the%20special%20day.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20got%20an%20ornament%20with%20our%20wedding%20date%20on%20it%20for%20the%20tree%2C%20started%20planning%20out%20a%20festive%20dinner%20for%20our%20family%2C%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20prioritize%20spending%20time%20together.%20Little%20things%20like%20these%20helped%20me%20reclaim%20the%20excitement%20of%20our%20first%20Christmas.%20I%20realized%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20myself%20%E2%80%94%20or%20my%20wife%20%E2%80%94%20to%20do%20big%20things%20each%20day%20to%20have%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fim-in-the-sandwich-generation-the-holidays-depend-on-me-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Especial%20holiday%20season%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20We%20could%20do%20simple%20things%2C%20like%20share%20quiet%20moments%20or%20cook%20new%20holiday%20dishes%20as%20a%20couple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20most%20excited%20to%20wake%20up%20on%20Christmas%20and%20have%20a%20private%20gift%20exchange%20(and%20not%20%3Cem%3Ejust%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecause%20I%20love%20presents).%20Seeing%20Taryn%20open%20her%20gift%20will%20bring%20me%20irreplaceable%20joy%2C%20which%20I'm%20excited%20to%20share%20with%20her%20as%20a%20married%20couple.%20We%20made%20our%20mission%20simple%3A%20pick%20out%20a%20new%20winter%20scarf%20we%20think%20the%20other%20will%20love.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20Christmas%20as%20newlyweds%20won't%20be%20the%20only%20one%20we%20spend%20together%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20special%20it%20feels.%20Romanticizing%20our%20first%20holiday%20was%20great%20in%20theory%20until%20it%20became%20a%20pressure%20cooker%20for%20perfection%20%E2%80%94%20decidedly%20unromantic.%20But%20in%20the%20process%20of%20reframing%20my%20mindset%2C%20I%20found%20that%20there%20was%20still%20magic%20and%20romance%20for%20the%20taking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewlywed-christmas-pressure-special-moments-together-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734866881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6762e09e6c531c315b88e909%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewlywed-christmas-pressure-special-moments-together-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20worried%20that%20our%20first%20Christmas%20as%20a%20married%20couple%20wouldn't%20be%20special%20enough.%20My%20wife%20helped%20me%20let%20go%20of%20the%20pressure%20and%20enjoy%20the%20season.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kylie%20Sapphino)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnewlywed-christmas-pressure-special-moments-together-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Samson%20Reveals%20Why%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20Went%20For%2013-Year-Old%20Suryavanshi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20standout%20moments%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202025%20mega%20auction%20was%20the%20bidding%20war%20for%2013-year-old%20batting%20wonderkid%20Vaibhav%20Suryavanshi.%20As%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20Suryavanshi%20became%20the%20youngest-ever%20player%20to%20be%20bought%20in%20an%20IPL%20auction%2C%20being%20sold%20to%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20(RR)%20for%20Rs%201.1%20crore.%20RR%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sanju%20Samson%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1701-sanju-samson-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESanju%20Samson%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20now%20revealed%20the%20thought%20process%20that%20led%20to%20the%20franchise%20bidding%20for%20the%2013-year-old%2C%20and%20stated%20that%20his%20purchase%20goes%20right%20in%20line%20with%20the%20philosophy%20and%20principles%20at%20Rajasthan%20Royals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20seen%20his%20highlights.%20All%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20decision-making%20group%20saw%20him%20bat%20at%20the%20U19%20Test%20match%20vs%20Australia%20in%20Chennai%2C%20where%20he%20scored%20a%20hundred%20of%2060-70%20balls.%20The%20shots%20that%20he%20played%20there%2C%20it%20felt%20like%2C%20that's%20something%20special%2C%26quot%3B%20Samson%20told%20South%20African%20cricket%20great%20%3Ca%