%20and%20services%20will%20also%20perform%20well%20independently%20of%20AI%2C%20making%20it%20a%20promising%20growth%20area%20for%20AI%20enthusiasts%20and%20skeptics%20alike.%20%26quot%3BSoftware%20%26amp%3B%20Services%20offers%20investors%20secular%20growth%20given%20it%20is%20the%20industry%20group%20least%20reliant%20on%20changes%20in%20economic%20growth%20or%20interest%20rates%20to%20drive%20share%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bank%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETruist%20sees%20robust%20underlying%20fundamentals%20and%20above-market%20earnings%20for%20businesses%20in%20the%20sector.%20The%20tech%20sector%20is%20home%20to%20many%20quality%20companies%20with%20strong%20business%20models%20and%20robust%20cash%20flow%2C%20according%20to%20UBS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c9f76b0-704d-444f-99d2-471a4708db36%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUtilities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirms%20optimistic%20about%20the%20sector%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EGoldman%20Sachs%2C%20JPMorgan%2C%20UBS%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsensus%20thesis%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20mostly-domestic%20industry%20will%20be%20shielded%20from%20tariffs%20and%20will%20benefit%20from%20AI%20tailwinds%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20sees%20utilities%20as%20a%20triple%20threat%3A%20the%20sector%20is%20defensive%20and%20will%20do%20well%20if%20economic%20growth%20slows%3B%20it's%20a%20beneficiary%20of%20AI's%20immense%20power%20demand%3B%20and%20its%20strong%20US%20presence%20reduces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-impact-on-inflation-tax-cut-policy-oil-prices-2024-12%3Futm_source%3DIterable%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_campaign%3D%2520Business%2520Insider%2520Today%2520-%2520December%252018%2C%25202024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20impact%20of%20potential%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sector%20is%2098%25%20domestic-facing%2C%20which%20should%20insulate%20it%20relative%20to%20peers%20in%20the%20event%20of%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20Sachs%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUBS%20echoed%20similar%20sentiments%20in%20its%202025%20outlook%3A%20%26quot%3BAlthough%20utilities%20companies%20with%20high%20renewables%20exposure%20could%20face%20near-term%20pressures%2C%20we%20also%20expect%20significant%20growth%20in%20AI%20data%20centers%20to%20fuel%20power%20demand%2C%20leading%20to%20higher%20power%20prices.%20Roughly%2020-25%25%20of%20the%20sector%20has%20material%20exposure%20to%20these%20trends.%20The%20sector's%20defensive%20characteristics%20should%20also%20offer%20ballast%20to%20a%20portfolio%20in%20case%20economic%20growth%20concerns%20rise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20utilities%20sector%20has%20historically%20led%20the%20charge%20in%20times%20of%20high%20M%26amp%3BA%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210b153f2-e2a7-42d3-9c39-bacccc3310fa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirms%20optimistic%20about%20the%20sector%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EBank%20of%20America%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsensus%20thesis%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cem%3ELow%20starting%20valuations%20provide%20opportunity%20to%20beat%20investor%20expectations%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20coming%20in%20second%20to%20last%20in%20performance%20this%20year%2C%20materials%20wasn't%20a%20popular%20pick%20among%20Wall%20Street%2C%20but%20Goldman%20Sachs%20and%20Bank%20of%20America%20are%20betting%20on%20the%20sector%20to%20make%20a%20comeback%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sector%20was%20battered%20this%20year%20by%20concerns%20about%20the%20Chinese%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20a%20major%20consumer%20of%20raw%20materials%20%E2%80%94%20and%20falling%20commodity%20prices%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sector's%20low%20starting%20valuation%20suggests%20some%20pessimism%20is%20already%20reflected%20in%20the%20stocks%20and%20that%20increases%20the%20likelihood%20for%20an%20asymmetric%20rise%20over%20a%2012-month%20time%20frame%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20Sachs%20strategists%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBank%20of%20America%20predicts%20over%2020%25%20of%20growth%20for%20the%20sector%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-sectors-wall-street-investing-advice-tips-technology-goldman-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734866521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67223eef9b3250dbbceb12bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-sectors-wall-street-investing-advice-tips-technology-goldman-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tech%20dominated%20market%20returns%20in%202024%2C%20but%20Wall%20Street%20is%20expecting%20more%20winners%20in%202025.%20Investors%20should%20be%20bullish%20on%20these%204%20sectors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cji%40businessinsider.com%20(Christine%20Ji)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A62%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-sectors-wall-street-investing-advice-tips-technology-goldman-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20student-loan%20borrower%20got%20%24155%2C000%20in%20debt%20wiped%20out%20through%20bankruptcy%20using%20new%20relief%20guidance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221079%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alrena%20Dale%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67659f1b5cddac6581d73e5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22809%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlrena%20Dale%20discharged%20%24155%2C000%20of%20her%20student%20loans%20in%20bankruptcy.%3Cp%3EAlrena%20Dale%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAlrena%20Dale%2C%2061%2C%20got%20%24155%2C000%20in%20student%20loans%20discharged%20through%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBiden's%20new%20bankruptcy%20guidance%2C%20aimed%20at%20easing%20the%20process%20for%20borrowers%2C%20made%20that%20possible.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20attorneys%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20new%20guidance%20is%20a%20big%20help%2C%20but%20more%20outreach%20would%20be%20helpful.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAlrena%20Dale%2C%2061%2C%20had%20her%20six-figure%20student-loan%20balance%20wiped%20out%20after%20decades%20of%20payments.%20She's%20one%20of%20hundreds%20of%20borrowers%20who%20have%20received%20relief%20after%20new%20changes%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-discharge-student-loan-debt-bankrtupcy-biden-reforms-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebankruptcy%20process%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Dale%20filed%20over%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20new%20bankruptcy%20guidance%2C%20which%20streamlined%20the%20information%20she%20needed%20to%20provide%20in%20order%20to%20qualify%20for%20relief%2C%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20her%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20Dale%20was%20finally%20relieved%20of%20her%20%24155%2C000%20balance%2C%20according%20to%20documents%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20no%20words.%20I%20was%20excited.%20I%20cried%2C%26quot%3B%20Dale%2C%20who'd%20attended%20an%20online%20business%20bachelor's%20and%20master's%20program%20but%20struggled%20to%20find%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eemployment%20in%20her%20field%2C%20told%20BI.%20She%20worked%20multiple%20minimum-wage%20jobs%20at%20a%20time%20to%20afford%20her%20student-loan%20payments%20alongside%20her%20monthly%20expenses.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20honestly%20didn't%20believe%20it%20until%20I%20got%20my%20discharge%20papers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20it%20was%20so%20difficult%20for%20Dale%20and%20many%20other%20student-loan%20borrowers%20to%20seek%20relief%20in%20bankruptcy%20court%20before%202022%20is%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eborrowers%20had%20to%20prove%20an%20%26quot%3Bundue%20hardship%26quot%3B%20standard%2C%20in%20which%20they%20had%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20show%20that%20they%20cannot%20maintain%20a%20minimal%20standard%20of%20living%2C%20that%20their%20circumstances%20aren't%20likely%20to%20improve%2C%20and%20that%20they%20have%20made%20a%20good-faith%20effort%20to%20repay%20their%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20standard%20was%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-bankruptcy-court-borrower-cancer-treatments-biden-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextremely%20high%20bar%20for%20borrowers%20to%20meet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Biden%20administration's%20guidance%20changed%20that%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-debt-cancellation-new-bankruptcy-guidance-justice-education-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestablishing%20clearer%20guidelines%20for%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20meet%20undue%20hardship%2C%20and%20it%20allowed%20borrowers%20to%20complete%20a%20self-attestation%20form%2C%20allowing%20the%20bankruptcy%20process%20to%20move%20quicker%20and%20avoid%20investigations%20into%20their%20backgrounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20bankruptcy%20attorneys%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20new%20guidance%20has%20made%20student-loan%20bankruptcy%20much%20more%20achievable%20for%20borrowers%2C%20with%20some%20having%20seen%20quick%20success%20after%20decades%20of%20stagnancy.%20Still%2C%20they%20said%20many%20lawyers%20are%20reluctant%20to%20lean%20into%20the%20new%20process%2C%20and%20more%20outreach%20and%20education%20on%20navigating%20bankruptcy%20for%20student%20loans%20would%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDale%20said%20the%20overwhelming%20emotion%20she%20now%20feels%20is%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKnowing%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20out%20and%20work%20a%20second%20job%20just%20to%20pay%20it%20back%20because%20they've%20removed%20it%20for%20me%2C%20I%20really%20can't%20thank%20them%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20Dale%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20words%20because%20I'm%20just%20happy%20and%20grateful%20and%20thankful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ca2b613d-24cb-4fe0-ae1f-15ba4815a959%5C%22%3E'It's%20given%20us%20so%20much%20hope'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBob%20and%20Tammy%20Branson%2C%20a%20bankruptcy%20attorney%20and%20senior%20paralegal%2C%20respectively%2C%20successfully%20represented%20Dale%20in%20her%20bankruptcy%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETammy%20said%20that%20over%20the%20past%2025%20years%2C%20it%20was%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20discharge%20their%20clients'%20student%20loans%20in%20bankruptcy%20%E2%80%94%20but%20after%20the%20new%20guidance%2C%20she%20said%20their%20law%20firm%20has%20successfully%20discharged%20over%20%241%20million%20in%20student%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20we're%20actually%20getting%20people%20not%20just%20to%20the%20point%20of%20treading%20water%2C%20but%20we're%20getting%20them%20out%20of%20the%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20Bob%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDustin%20Baker%2C%20a%20bankruptcy%20attorney%20in%20Iowa%2C%20has%20seen%20similar%20success%20with%20the%20new%20guidance.%20Baker%20told%20BI%20that%20before%20November%202022%2C%20he%20advised%20his%20clients%20that%20considering%20a%20student-loan%20discharge%20wasn't%20worth%20their%20effort%20because%20it%20was%20so%20difficult%20to%20achieve%2C%20and%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20take%20his%20clients'%20money%20for%20litigation%20he%20wasn't%20confident%20would%20be%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20once%20the%20guidance%20was%20announced%2C%20Baker%20said%20he's%20eliminated%20student%20debt%20for%20about%20a%20dozen%20of%20his%20clients%2C%20with%20a%20few%20more%20in%20the%20pipeline.%20He%20said%20his%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20excitement%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20new%20process%20is%20the%20self-attestation%20form%2C%20which%20directly%20tells%20borrowers%20the%20questions%20they%20need%20to%20answer%20to%20get%20approved%20for%20a%20discharge%2C%20making%20communication%20between%20the%20borrower%20and%20the%20government%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%20released%20new%20data%20in%20July%20on%20how%20the%20process%20was%20going%20since%20the%20new%20guidance%20was%20announced.%20It%20showed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-debt-cancellation-new-bankruptcy-guidance-justice-education-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E588%20new%20cases%20were%20filed%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20October%202023%20to%20March%202024%20%E2%80%94%20a%2034%25%20increase%20from%20the%20prior%206-month%20period.%20New%20data%20BI%20obtained%20from%20Sen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%20in%20October%20showed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-discharge-debt-bankruptcy-court-guidance-elizabeth-warren-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%20900%20borrowers%20sought%20out%20the%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20fiscal%20year%202024%2C%20and%2085%25%20of%20borrowers%20who%20filed%20using%20the%20new%20guidance%20received%20a%20full%20or%20partial%20discharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaker%20said%20his%20experience%20incorporating%20the%20new%20guidance%20into%20his%20work%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20added%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emembers%20of%20the%20Justice%20Department%20gave%20attorneys%20in%20his%20area%20training%20sessions.%20However%2C%20Tammy%20and%20Bob%20said%20more%20education%20and%20outreach%20would%20be%20helpful%20because%20some%20lawyers%20are%20unsure%20if%20the%20new%20process%20is%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it's%20clear%20the%20guidance%20works%2C%20and%20Tammy%20said%20she%20hopes%20that%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20given%20us%20so%20much%20hope%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d02f473-829d-42da-9687-603292dcfb0c%5C%22%3E'I%20would've%20had%20to%20work%20another%20job'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20bankruptcy%20process%20for%20student-loan%20borrowers%20still%20isn't%20perfect.%20Igor%20Roitburg%2C%20a%20former%20attorney%20and%20senior%20managing%20director%20at%20Stretto%20%E2%80%94%20a%20bankruptcy%20services%20and%20technology%20firm%20%E2%80%94%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20timeline%20for%20borrowers%20to%20receive%20a%20bankruptcy%20decision%20can%20still%20widely%20vary%20and%20that%20uncertainty%20is%20a%20roadblock%20for%20some%20borrowers%20and%20attorneys%20to%20participate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20them%20to%20invest%20time%20and%20effort%20into%20a%20new%20process%20that%20they're%20uncertain%20about%20if%20they%20don't%20see%20results%20for%20months%20and%20months%20and%20months%2C%20makes%20it%20hard%20for%20them%20to%20commit%20to%20the%20process%20and%20offer%20it%20as%20a%20global%20service%20to%20all%20their%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20Roitburg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDale%20said%20she%20saw%20no%20other%20option%20but%20to%20file%20for%20bankruptcy%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20it%20would%20be%20successful.%20Once%20the%20new%20guidance%20was%20released%2C%20the%20self-attestation%20form%20allowed%20Dale%20to%20prove%20that%20her%20financial%20circumstances%20were%20unlikely%20to%20improve%2C%20qualifying%20her%20for%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20now%20works%20at%20a%20call%20center%20and%20said%20she%20can't%20afford%20to%20retire%20yet.%20If%20she%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20do%20things%20differently%2C%20she%20might%20have%20considered%20going%20to%20a%20trade%20school%20to%20avoid%20the%20student-debt%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20just%20making%20the%20best%20of%20what%20I%20have%20to%20work%20with%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20if%20she%20didn't%20see%20success%20through%20bankruptcy%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would've%20had%20to%20work%20another%20job%20just%20to%20pay%20the%20student%20loans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%