aybe%20that%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20he%20is%20looking%20to%20play%20over%20there%20and%20gets%20out.%20If%20you%20see%2C%20it's%20not%20that%20he%20has%20opened%20the%20face%20of%20the%20bat.%20It's%20not%20that%20he%20is%20looking%20to%20play%20to%20the%20covers.%20If%20that%20was%20happening%2C%20then%20you%20could%20say%2C%20hey%2C%20don't%20play%20towards%20cover.%20But%20it's%20a%20shot%20that%20has%20got%20him%20thousands%20of%20runs.%20Only%20this%20time%2C%20maybe%20the%20late%20movement%20is%20getting%20him%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20what%20Kohli%20could%20do%20on%20the%20field%20to%20prevent%20himself%20from%20getting%20out%20in%20the%20same%20manner%20again%2C%20Gavaskar%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThat's%20up%20to%20him.%20It%20is%20really%20up%20to%20him%2C%20what%20he%20does.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20you%20don't%20score%20X%20thousand%20runs%20in%20international%20cricket%20and%20get%20that%20many%20hundreds%20unless%20you%20know%20how%20to%20approach%20and%20build%20a%20Test%20innings.%20I%20am%20sure%20this%20one%20week%20will%20give%20him%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20look%20at%20his%20dismissals.%20More%20than%20the%20dismissals%2C%20I%20would%20like%20him%20and%20even%20Rohit%20(Sharma%2C%20the%20captain)%20to%20look%20at%20all%20the%20innings%20where%20they%20have%20scored%20brilliant%20centuries.%20That%20is%20what%20is%20going%20to%20make%20them%20start%20believing.%20I%20want%20that%20positivity%20to%20come%20into%20their%20thinking%20rather%20than%20them%20thinking%20only%20about%20getting%20out%20to%20deliveries%20that%20are%20on%20the%20off-stump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734865140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fnepmpbpg_sunil-gavaskar-bcci_625x300_05_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fsunil-gavaskars-unflinching-message-as-virat-kohli-struggles-for-form-7306252%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22S