-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAman%20Kumar%20and%20his%20co-founder%20pose%20with%20farmers%20at%20their%20primary%20processing%20space%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20that%20solution%20in%20200%20liters%20of%20water.%20The%20results%20have%20been%20quite%20good.%20The%20yield%20has%20improved%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F374594%2Fwinter-soil-health-india-tips-farmers-temperature-crops-compaction-microbial-activity%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoil%20has%20become%20softer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20pH%20of%20our%20soil%2C%20which%20was%208.5%2C%20is%20now%20down%20to%207.5.%20We%E2%80%99re%20all%20working%20very%20hard%20to%20make%20it%20even%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20primary%20processing%20infrastructure%20was%20established%2C%20Aman%20envisioned%20a%20future%20beyond%20mere%20raw%20material%20supply.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20secondary%20processing%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20take%20this%20enterprise%20to%20newer%20heights%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20Recognising%20the%20growing%20demand%20for%20clean%2C%20preservative-free%20peanut%20butter%20in%20urban%20areas%2C%20he%20embarked%20on%20developing%20his%20own%20unique%20product.%20After%20months%20of%20experimentation%2C%20he%20formulated%20a%20healthy%20peanut%20butter%20that%20would%20appeal%20to%20health-conscious%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20support%20of%20a%20grant%20from%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Government%20and%20a%20contribution%20of%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20from%20Anuj%20Sharma%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20TISS%2C%20Aman%20was%20able%20to%20purchase%20the%20necessary%20machinery%20and%20start%20producing%20peanut%20butter.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20promoting%20the%20local%20peanut%20variety%2C%20food%20security%2C%20and%20transparency%20in%20our%20ingredients%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aman%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Nutty%20Village%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20empowering%20rural%20communities%20didn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20there.%20To%20further%20enhance%20women%E2%80%99s%20participation%2C%20they%20collaborated%20with%20the%20National%20Rural%20Livelihood%20Mission%20to%20form%20Self-Help%20Groups%20(SHGs).%20These%20SHGs%20provided%20women%20with%20access%20to%20peanut%20shelling%20machines%2C%20training%20them%20in%20the%20necessary%20skills%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20secondary%20processing%20of%20groundnuts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandkali%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20member%20of%20the%20self-help%20group%2C%20reflects%20on%20how%20her%20life%20has%20changed%20through%20their%20collective%20efforts.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20I%20mostly%20worked%20at%20home.%20The%20societal%20structure%20didn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20women%20to%20be%20out%20earning%2C%20and%20many%20like%20me%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%20phone%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20However%2C%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20Nutty%20Village%20and%20being%20involved%20in%20secondary%20processing%2C%20has%20empowered%20her%20in%20unexpected%20ways.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20Aman%20calls%20us%20for%20work%20with%20peanuts%2C%20we%20go%2C%20and%20we%20earn%20a%20good%20amount.%20The%20group%20I%20am%20in%20feels%20like%20a%20community%2C%20like%20a%20union.%20When%20we%20get%20work%2C%20we%20all%20benefit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20have%20to%20travel%20to%20nearby%20towns%20for%20higher%20wages%2C%20Chandkali%20is%20content%20to%20stay%20close%20to%20home.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20make%20300%20rupees%20per%20day%20here.%20If%20I%20had%20to%20go%20far%20for%20work%2C%20being%20a%20woman%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20been%20able%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EConquering%20the%20hurdles%20to%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAman%20and%20his%20team%E2%80%99s%20journey%20was%20not%20without%20challenges.%20From%20persuading%20farmers%20to%20embrace%20new%20agricultural%20techniques%20to%20navigating%20complex%20bureaucratic%20processes%2C%20they%20encountered%20numerous%20obstacles.%20One%20significant%20hurdle%20was%20securing%20an%20electricity%20connection%20for%20their%20machinery%20unit%2C%20which%20involved%20navigating%20a%20labyrinth%20of%20bureaucratic%20red%20tape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20now%20have%20electricity%20connection%2C%20license%2C%20quality%20control%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20is%20because%20I%20am%20CSIR%20incubated.%20I%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20connections%20back%20in%20college%20and%20when%20I%20was%20working%20for%20Fresh-ily%2C%20But%20the%20farmers%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20that%20for%20themselves.%20Even%20if%20they%20do%20want%20to%20start%20or%20scale%20their%20business%2C%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20pay%20Rs%2060%2C000%20just%20to%20get%20an%20electricity%20connection.%20This%20needs%20to%20change%20at%20a%20policy%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aman%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20us%20too%2C%20we%20won%20a%20lot%20of%20grants%2C%20but%20it%20would%20take%20seven%20to%20eight%20months%20for%20the%20other%20installments%20to%20come%20in.%20As%20a%20founder%2C%20I%20can%20stretch%20out%20a%20few%20months%20but%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20expect%20my%20team%20of%20farmers%20to%20just%20wait%20for%20funding%20that%20was%20promised%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aman%2C%20reflecting%20on%20the%20stress%20of%20managing%20cash%20flow%20during%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20the%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-16-at-10.22.27-PM_11zon-1734607528-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20farmer%20harvests%20peanuts%20from%20the%20ground%2C%20carefully%20pulling%20the%20plants%20to%20collect%20the%20fresh%20cr