d%2C%20carefully%20pulling%20the%20plants%20to%20collect%20the%20fresh%20crop%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20these%20hurdles%2C%20Nutty%20Village%20has%20witnessed%20remarkable%20growth%20in%20recent%20years.%20Revenue%20surged%20from%20Rs%2060%2C000%20in%202022%20to%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20in%202023%2C%20and%20is%20projected%20to%20reach%20Rs%2013-15%20lakh%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20transformation%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20power%20of%20collaboration%20and%20innovative%20solutions.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20getting%20better%20prices%20for%20each%20kilogram%20of%20peanuts%20we%20sell%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20see%20a%20real%20improvement%20in%20our%20seasonal%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aditya%20Sengar%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Unnao%2C%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWorking%20with%20people%20who%20have%20seen%20the%20world%2C%20and%20studied%20these%20things%20has%20also%20helped%20us%20bring%20in%20fresh%20ideas%20to%20farming%2C%20learn%20about%20modern%20techniques%2C%20and%20open%20up%20new%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20further%20expand%20their%20impact%2C%20Nutty%20Village%20is%20collaborating%20with%20the%20Chief%20Development%20Officer%20to%20map%20500%20hectares%20of%20land%20for%20a%20proposed%20peanut%20farming%20cluster.%20This%20initiative%20will%20not%20only%20provide%20farmers%20with%20recognition%20but%20also%20offer%20crucial%20support%20services.%20Once%20recognised%20as%20a%20cluster%2C%20farmers%20will%20gain%20better%20access%20to%20markets%2C%20strengthening%20their%20position%20and%20enabling%20them%20to%20achieve%20greater%20prosperity.%20Currently%2C%20the%20producer%20group%20comprises%2050%20farmers%2C%20but%20the%20ambitious%20cluster%20development%20plan%20aims%20to%20unite%202%2C000%20farmers%2C%20creating%20a%20powerful%20collective%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20biggest%20issue%20we%20see%20around%20the%20world%20is%20that%20farmers%20aren%E2