%20and%20open%20to%20everyone.%20These%20walks%20offer%20a%20chance%20to%20rediscover%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20hidden%20heritage%20through%20landmarks%20like%20Ulsoor%20Lake%2C%20Cubbon%20Park%2C%20and%20Nandi%20Durg.%20They%20have%20even%20prepared%20treasure%20cues%20to%20make%20the%20experience%20more%20engaging%2C%20and%20taken%20the%20lead%20in%20getting%20all%20this%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sreeja%20says%20with%20a%20proud%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESparkling%20Mindz%20students%20were%20just%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20performing%20snippets%20of%20%3Cem%3EBengaluru%2C%20Once%20a%20City%20of%20Lakes%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20different%20corners%20of%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20like%20we%20were%20translating%20the%20lake%E2%80%99s%20emotions%20into%20human%20language%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sabreesh%2C%20another%20student%2C%20says.%20His%20benchmate%2C%20Nikhil%2C%20adds%20that%20they%20had%20even%20started%20work%20in%20the%20school%2C%20like%20creating%20recharge%20pits%20and%20making%20arrangements%20for%20water%20harvesting%2C%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20were%20water-sufficient%20in%20the%20face%20of%20another%20water%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20who%20knew%20that%20not%20many%20months%20later%2C%20they%20would%20be%20listening%20to%20Mihika%20share%20her%20story%20about%20how%20floods%20in%20the%20city%20made%20her%20miss%20her%20Trinity%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202943px)%20100vw%2C%202943px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FTRUI-Team-1-1_11zon-1734349588.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222943%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sparkling%20Mindz%20students%20ready%20to%20host%20a%20waste%20managerment%20stall%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FTRUI-Team-1-1_11zon-1734349588.jpg%202943w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FTRUI-Team-1-1_11z