e%20with%20river%20sand%20and%20pebbles.%20This%20sand%20is%20watered%20twice%20a%20day.%20This%20keeps%20the%20produce%20cool.%20Each%20unit%20benefits%20over%20120%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Binolin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Binolin%20Syiemlieh%2C%20centre%20manager%20at%20the%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%2C%20says%20their%20non-profit%20has%20set%20up%20simple%2C%20small-scale%2C%20zero-energy%20storage%20units%20near%20farmers%E2%80%99%20fields%20to%20preserve%20their%20produce.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-5-1733815262-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388012%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBinolin%20Syiemlieh%2C%20centre%20manager%20at%20the%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%2C%20says%20their%20non-profit%20has%20set%20up%20simple%2C%20small-scale%2C%20zero-energy%20storage%20units%20near%20farmers%E2%80%99%20fields%20to%20preserve%20their%20produce%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Nongstoin%20Social%20Service%20Society%20(NSSS)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20cold%20storage%20units%2C%20though%20rooted%20in%20scientific%20principles%2C%20involve%20no%20elaborate%20technology.%20They%20are%20managed%20by%20the%20Village%20Executive%20Committee%20(VEC)%2C%20ensuring%20equitable%20access%20for%20all%20villagers%20while%20keeping%20produce%20clean%20and%20fresh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20is%20funded%20by%20the%20Meghalaya%20Basin%20Management%20Agency%20(MBMA)%2C%20a%20not-for-profit%20organisation%20handling%20externally%20aided%20government%20projects.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20initiative%20is%20supported%20by%20the%20World%20Bank%20under%20an%20innovation%20fund%20that%20helps%20improve%20or%20scale%20up%20solutions.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Community-Led%20Landscape%20Management%20Project%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20addressing%20natural%20resource%20management%20issues%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Wankit%20Swer%2C%20general%20manager%20at%20MBMA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20farmers%20are%20smallholders%20with%20limited%20production.%20After%20meeting%20their%20own%20needs%2C%20the%20excess%20is%20sold.%20Without%20proper%20storage%2C%20they%20often%20resort%20to%20distress%20sales%20of%20perishable%20items.%20These%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F314446%2Fchennai-student-eco-friendly-tech-increases-produce-shelf-life-sunharvested-coolrooms%2F%5C%22%3Ecold%20storage%20units%3C%2Fa%3E%20prevent%20such%20sales%20and%20provide%20a%20better%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Anti-microbial%20fabric%20made%20from%20banana%20fibre%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagaland-based%20venture%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%20is%20making%20remarkable%20progress%20in%20harnessing%20banana%20fibre.%20%E2%80%9COur%20banana%20fibre%20project%20is%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Runway%20India%E2%80%99%20division%20of%20our%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Major%20Tanay%20Maben%2C%20co-founder%20of%20the%20venture.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20currently%20in%20the%20research%20and%20development%20(R%26amp%3BD)%20phase%2C%20working%20on%20producing%20fabric%20from%20banana%20fibre%2C%20which%20boasts%20anti-microbial%20properties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20anti-microbial%20properties%20of%20banana%20fibre%2C%20derived%20from%20natural%20compounds%20in%20the%20plant%2C%20create%20a%20protective%20shield%20on%20the%20fabric%2C%20inhibiting%20the%20growth%20of%20bacteria%20and%20fungi.%20This%20fabric%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20used%20in%20medical%20textiles%2C%20and%20efforts%20are%20underway%20to%20integrate%20additional%20functional%20properties%2C%20such%20as%20water%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nengneithem%20Hengna%20(L)%20and%20Major%20Tanay%20Maben%20(R)%20-%20co-founders%20of%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-9-1733816042-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388032%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENengneithem%20Hengna%20(L)%20and%20Major%20Tanay%20Maben%20(R)%20%E2%80%93%20co-founders%20of%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20Hengna%20%26amp%3B%20Maben%20Private%20Limited%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354933%2Fombak-sustainable-furniture-shruthi-prakash-rattan-chairs-table-wall-decor-from-banana-fibres-in-indonesia-india%2F%5C%22%3EBanana%20fibre%20is%20also%20an%20eco-friendly%20alternative%20to%20polymer-based%20fabrics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20it%20is%20biodegradable.%20Moreover%2C%20banana%20plants%20require%20minimal%20water%20and%20chemical%20inputs%2C%20including%20pesticides%20and%20fertilisers%2C%20making%20them%20a%20sustainable%20option%20compared%20to%20water-intensive%20cotton%2C%20explains%20Major%20Tanay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20company%20produces%20handicrafts%20and%20packaging%20materials%20using%20banana%20fibre.%20With%20the%20goal%20of%20establishing%20banana%20fibre%20as%20a%20signature%20product%20of%20Nagaland%2C%20it%20has%20trained%20700%20artisans%20across%20Nagaland%20and%20other%20Northeast%20Indian%20states%20to%20create%20handmade%20items%20from%20the%20fibre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fho_0vUAs4-w%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%2C%20Nengneithem%20Hengna%2C%20who%20brings%2013%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20handicrafts%20sector%2C%20began%20working%20with%20banana%20fibre%20in%202019.%20She%20experimented%20with%20different%20grades%20of%20fibre%2C%20braiding%20techniques%2C%20and%20stitching%20methods.%20She%20met%20Major%20Maben%20during%20COVID%20relief%20efforts%2C%20and%20they%20discovered%20shared%20goals.%20This%20collaboration%20led%20to%20the%20official%20incorporation%20of%20the%20company%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBanana%20is%20a%20zero-waste%20cash%20crop%20which%20yields%20a%20variety%20of%20products%20and%20by-products%20within%20a%20year%20of%20planting.%20It%20grows%20well%20in%20gently%20sloping%20terrain%20and%20is%20low-maintenance.%20Also%2C%20banana%20fibre%20is%20a%20very%20versatile%20fibre%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Major%20Tanay.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20coarser%20type%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20coasters%20while%20the%20delicate%20variety%20can%20be%20used%20to%20craft%20jewellery%20and%20hair%20extensions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trained%20artisans%20across%20Nagaland%20and%20other%20Northeast%20Indian%20states%20create%20handmade%20items%20from%20banana%20fibre.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FUntitled-design-6-1733816156-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-388038%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETrained%20artisans%20across%20Nagaland%20and